      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-72 h-72 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 to-teal-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm mb-8 animate-fade-in-down">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
        <span class="font-medium">Kami Siap Membantu</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-poppins animate-fade-in-up">
        Hubungi Kami
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up">
        Mari berbicara tentang proyek Anda. Tim kami siap membantu mewujudkan solusi digital yang tepat untuk bisnis Anda.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
